UseBB Development Version Upgrading
-----------------------------------

Current version: 0.4

* Upgrading from 0.3.x:
	Run install/upgrade-0-3.php in your web browser.

* Upgrading from 0.2.3(a):
	To upgrade, run install/upgrade-0-2-3.php and install/upgrade-0-3.php in your web browser.

* Upgrading from 0.2.2 or earlier:
	First upgrade to 0.2.3a, then run install/upgrade-0-2-3.php and install/upgrade-0-3.php.
